      "content": "<h1>🏆 MISP Challenge 2026</h1>\n<p>Audio-Visual-Text Multimodal Keyword Spotting Challenge</p>\n\n<h2>📋 Overview</h2>\n<p>This competition focuses on audio-visual-text multimodal keyword spotting task in realistic speech processing scenarios.</p>\n\n<h3>Task Description</h3>\n<p>Your model needs to determine whether given audio-video pairs come from the same speaker and the same keyword.</p>\n\n<h3>inset vs outset</h3>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Term</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Description</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><strong>inset</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Keywords seen during training</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><strong>outset</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">New keywords not seen during training</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>Evaluation Metrics</h3>\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>AUC_INSET</h4>\n        <p>AUC on inset keywords<br><small>Higher is better</small></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>EER_INSET</h4>\n        <p>EER on inset (%)<br><small>Lower is better</small></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>AUC_OUTSET</h4>\n        <p>AUC on outset keywords<br><small>Higher is better</small></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>EER_OUTSET</h4>\n        <p>EER on outset (%)<br><small>Lower is better</small></p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>🚀 Quick Start - 5 Steps to Submit</h2>\n<div style=\"display: grid; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">1</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>Generate Predictions</strong>\n            <p>Run your model on the test set and collect prediction results</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">2</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>Prepare CSV</strong>\n            <p>Save predictions in the required CSV format</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">3</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>Compress CSV</strong>\n            <p>Directly compress CSV file to zip format</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">4</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>Upload to Codabench</strong>\n            <p>Submit your zip file on this platform</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">5</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>View Results</strong>\n            <p>Wait for scoring and check the leaderboard!</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>⚠️ Important Update:</strong>\n    <p>You do NOT need to submit code or models! Only a CSV file with your predictions is required.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📊 Metric Interpretation</h2>\n<h3>AUC (Area Under Curve)</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li>Value Range: 0.0 - 1.0</li>\n    <li>Perfect Score: 1.0</li>\n    <li>Random Score: 0.5</li>\n    <li>Higher AUC indicates better model discrimination ability</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>EER (Equal Error Rate)</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li>Value Range: 0% - 100%</li>\n    <li>Perfect Score: 0%</li>\n    <li>Random Score: 50%</li>\n    <li>Lower EER indicates better model balance performance</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>📞 Technical Support</h2>\n<p>If you encounter issues during submission, please check the <strong>Data & Submission Guide</strong> tab or use the competition forum.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h1>🏆 MISP Challenge 2026</h1>\n<p>音频-视频-文本多模态关键词检测竞赛</p>\n\n<h2>📋 竞赛概述</h2>\n<p>本次竞赛聚焦于真实语音处理场景下的音频-视频-文本多模态关键词检测任务。</p>\n\n<h3>任务简介</h3>\n<p>您的模型需要判断给定的音频-视频对是否来自同一说话人和同一关键词。</p>\n\n<h3>inset vs outset</h3>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">术语</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">说明</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><strong>inset</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">训练时见过的词汇</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><strong>outset</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">训练时未见过的新词汇</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>评价指标</h3>\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>AUC_INSET</h4>\n        <p>inset词汇的AUC<br><small>越高越好</small></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>EER_INSET</h4>\n        <p>inset词汇的EER (%)<br><small>越低越好</small></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>AUC_OUTSET</h4>\n        <p>outset词汇的AUC<br><small>越高越好</small></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;\">\n        <h4>EER_OUTSET</h4>\n        <p>outset词汇的EER (%)<br><small>越低越好</small></p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>🚀 快速入门 - 5步完成提交</h2>\n<div style=\"display: grid; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">1</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>生成预测</strong>\n            <p>在测试集上运行您的模型，收集预测结果</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">2</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>准备CSV</strong>\n            <p>按照要求格式保存预测结果为CSV</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">3</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>压缩CSV</strong>\n            <p>直接将CSV文件压缩为zip格式</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">4</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>上传到Codabench</strong>\n            <p>在此平台提交您的zip文件</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 8px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: #667eea; color: white; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;\">5</div>\n        <div>\n            <strong>查看结果</strong>\n            <p>等待评分，查看排行榜！</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>⚠️ 重要更新:</strong>\n    <p>您不需要提交代码和模型！只需提交预测结果的CSV文件即可。</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📊 指标解读</h2>\n<h3>AUC (Area Under Curve)</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li>取值范围: 0.0 - 1.0</li>\n    <li>完美分数: 1.0</li>\n    <li>随机分数: 0.5</li>\n    <li>AUC越高表示模型的区分能力越好</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>EER (Equal Error Rate)</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li>取值范围: 0% - 100%</li>\n    <li>完美分数: 0%</li>\n    <li>随机分数: 50%</li>\n    <li>EER越低表示模型的平衡性能越好</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>📞 技术支持</h2>\n<p>如果在提交过程中遇到问题，请查看<strong>数据与提交指南</strong>标签页，或使用竞赛论坛。</p>",
