      "title": "data",
      "content": "<h1>📊 Data & Submission Guide</h1>\n<p>Complete guide for data format and submission requirements</p>\n\n<h2>📁 Submission Requirements</h2>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong>\n    <p>You only need to submit a zip file containing ONE CSV file. No code or model files required!</p>\n</div>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">File</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Required</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Description</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>predictions.csv</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">✅ Required</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Your prediction results (any filename ending with .csv works)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>submission.zip</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">✅ Required</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Zip file containing only the CSV file</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>📝 CSV Format Specification</h2>\n\n<h3>Required Columns</h3>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Column Name</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Type</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Description</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>id</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Integer</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Sample index, starting from 0</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>type</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">String</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Must be either <code>\"inset\"</code> or <code>\"outset\"</code></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>prediction</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Float</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">Prediction score between 0.0 and 1.0</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>Important Rules</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>id Numbering:</strong> Both inset and outset must start from 0 and be numbered separately</li>\n    <li><strong>Prediction Scores:</strong> Must be float values between 0.0 and 1.0 representing match probability\n        <ul>\n            <li>Closer to 1 means more likely to be a match</li>\n            <li>Closer to 0 means less likely to be a match</li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><strong>Sample Order:</strong> Prediction order must strictly match the test set order</li>\n    <li><strong>Completeness:</strong> Must include predictions for all test samples</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>CSV Example</h3>\n<pre style=\"background: #f4f4f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; margin: 15px 0;\">\nid,type,prediction\n0,inset,0.85\n1,inset,0.12\n2,inset,0.95\n3,inset,0.34\n...\n99,inset,0.67\n0,outset,0.45\n1,outset,0.78\n2,outset,0.23\n...\n99,outset,0.56\n</pre>\n\n<h2>💻 How to Generate Prediction CSV</h2>\n\n<h3>Python Code Example</h3>\n<pre style=\"background: #f4f4f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; margin: 15px 0;\">\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef generate_predictions_csv(inset_predictions, outset_predictions, output_file=\"predictions.csv\"):\n    \"\"\"\n    Generate CSV file for competition submission\n\n    Args:\n        inset_predictions: list/array, inset prediction scores (0-1 between)\n        outset_predictions: list/array, outset prediction scores (0-1 between)\n        output_file: output filename\n    \"\"\"\n    data = []\n\n    # Add inset predictions\n    for i, pred in enumerate(inset_predictions):\n        data.append({\n            'id': i,\n            'type': 'inset',\n            'prediction': pred\n        })\n\n    # Add outset predictions\n    for i, pred in enumerate(outset_predictions):\n        data.append({\n            'id': i,\n            'type': 'outset',\n            'prediction': pred\n        })\n\n    # Create DataFrame and save\n    df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n    df.to_csv(output_file, index=False)\n\n    print(f\"✅ Prediction CSV generated: {output_file}\")\n    print(f\"   - inset samples: {len(inset_predictions)}\")\n    print(f\"   - outset samples: {len(outset_predictions)}\")\n    print(f\"   - Total samples: {len(data)}\")\n\n    return df\n\n# Usage example\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # Replace with your actual predictions\n    num_inset = 100   # Replace with actual number of inset samples\n    num_outset = 100  # Replace with actual number of outset samples\n\n    my_inset_preds = np.random.rand(num_inset)   # Replace with your predictions\n    my_outset_preds = np.random.rand(num_outset) # Replace with your predictions\n\n    # Generate CSV\n    generate_predictions_csv(my_inset_preds, my_outset_preds, \"predictions.csv\")\n</pre>\n\n<h3>Prediction Value Notes</h3>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #22c55e; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>✅ Correct Prediction Values:</strong>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Floats between 0.0 and 1.0</li>\n        <li>Probability values after sigmoid or softmax</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>❌ Incorrect Prediction Values:</strong>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Negative numbers: -0.1</li>\n        <li>Numbers greater than 1: 1.5</li>\n        <li>Logits (not through sigmoid): 2.3, -1.2</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📤 How to Submit</h2>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 15px 15px 15px 30px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <h3>Submission Steps</h3>\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong>Prepare CSV File:</strong> Generate predictions.csv following the instructions above</li>\n        <li><strong>Compress File:</strong> Compress the CSV file to zip format\n            <ul>\n                <li>Windows: Right-click CSV file → Send to → Compressed (zipped) folder</li>\n                <li>Mac/Linux: <code>zip submission.zip predictions.csv</code></li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li><strong>Upload to Codabench:</strong> Click \"Submit\" button and upload your zip file</li>\n        <li><strong>Wait for Processing:</strong> Platform will automatically process your submission</li>\n        <li><strong>View Results:</strong> After processing is complete, results will appear on the leaderboard</li>\n    </ol>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>⚠️ Important Notes:</strong>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Ensure the zip contains only one CSV file</li>\n        <li>Do not include folders in the zip</li>\n        <li>Ensure CSV format is correct</li>\n        <li>Prediction order must be correct</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📥 Downloads</h2>\n<div style=\"background: #e7f3ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n    <h3>Available Downloads</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li><strong>Test Dataset</strong> - Preprocessed test data</li>\n        <li><strong>Sample Predictions</strong> - Example CSV file showing correct format</li>\n        <li><strong>Example Code</strong> - Python script for generating submission CSV</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h1>📊 数据与提交指南</h1>\n<p>数据格式和提交要求的完整指南</p>\n\n<h2>📁 提交要求</h2>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>⚠️ 重要:</strong>\n    <p>您只需要提交一个包含CSV文件的zip文件！不需要提交代码或模型文件！</p>\n</div>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">文件</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">必需</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">说明</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>predictions.csv</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">✅ 必需</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">您的预测结果（任何以.csv结尾的文件名都可以）</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>submission.zip</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">✅ 必需</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">只包含CSV文件的zip文件</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>📝 CSV格式说明</h2>\n\n<h3>必需列</h3>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">列名</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">类型</th>\n            <th style=\"background: #11998e; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">说明</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>id</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">整数</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">样本编号，从0开始</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>type</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">字符串</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">必须是 <code>\"inset\"</code> 或 <code>\"outset\"</code></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\"><code>prediction</code></td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">浮点数</td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left;\">0.0到1.0之间的预测分数</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>重要规则</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>id编号:</strong> inset和outset必须分别从0开始编号</li>\n    <li><strong>预测分数:</strong> 必须是0.0到1.0之间的浮点数，表示匹配概率\n        <ul>\n            <li>越接近1表示越可能匹配</li>\n            <li>越接近0表示越不可能匹配</li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><strong>样本顺序:</strong> 预测顺序必须严格与测试集顺序一致</li>\n    <li><strong>完整性:</strong> 必须包含所有测试样本的预测</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>CSV示例</h3>\n<pre style=\"background: #f4f4f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; margin: 15px 0;\">\nid,type,prediction\n0,inset,0.85\n1,inset,0.12\n2,inset,0.95\n3,inset,0.34\n...\n99,inset,0.67\n0,outset,0.45\n1,outset,0.78\n2,outset,0.23\n...\n99,outset,0.56\n</pre>\n\n<h2>💻 如何生成预测CSV</h2>\n\n<h3>Python代码示例</h3>\n<pre style=\"background: #f4f4f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; margin: 15px 0;\">\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef generate_predictions_csv(inset_predictions, outset_predictions, output_file=\"predictions.csv\"):\n    \"\"\"\n    生成竞赛提交用的CSV文件\n\n    参数:\n        inset_predictions: list/array，inset的预测分数（0-1之间）\n        outset_predictions: list/array，outset的预测分数（0-1之间）\n        output_file: 输出文件名\n    \"\"\"\n    data = []\n\n    # 添加inset预测\n    for i, pred in enumerate(inset_predictions):\n        data.append({\n            'id': i,\n            'type': 'inset',\n            'prediction': pred\n        })\n\n    # 添加outset预测\n    for i, pred in enumerate(outset_predictions):\n        data.append({\n            'id': i,\n            'type': 'outset',\n            'prediction': pred\n        })\n\n    # 创建DataFrame并保存\n    df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n    df.to_csv(output_file, index=False)\n\n    print(f\"✅ 预测CSV已生成: {output_file}\")\n    print(f\"   - inset样本数: {len(inset_predictions)}\")\n    print(f\"   - outset样本数: {len(outset_predictions)}\")\n    print(f\"   - 总样本数: {len(data)}\")\n\n    return df\n\n# 使用示例\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 替换为您的实际预测\n    num_inset = 100   # 替换为实际的inset样本数\n    num_outset = 100  # 替换为实际的outset样本数\n\n    my_inset_preds = np.random.rand(num_inset)   # 替换为您的预测\n    my_outset_preds = np.random.rand(num_outset) # 替换为您的预测\n\n    # 生成CSV\n    generate_predictions_csv(my_inset_preds, my_outset_preds, \"predictions.csv\")\n</pre>\n\n<h3>预测值注意事项</h3>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #22c55e; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>✅ 正确的预测值:</strong>\n    <ul>\n        <li>0.0到1.0之间的浮点数</li>\n        <li>经过sigmoid或softmax后的概率值</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>❌ 错误的预测值:</strong>\n    <ul>\n        <li>负数: -0.1</li>\n        <li>大于1的数: 1.5</li>\n        <li>logits（未经过sigmoid）: 2.3, -1.2</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📤 如何提交</h2>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 15px 15px 15px 30px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <h3>提交步骤</h3>\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong>准备CSV文件:</strong> 按照上述说明生成predictions.csv</li>\n        <li><strong>压缩文件:</strong> 将CSV文件压缩为zip格式\n            <ul>\n                <li>Windows: 右键CSV文件 → 发送到 → 压缩(zipped)文件夹</li>\n                <li>Mac/Linux: <code>zip submission.zip predictions.csv</code></li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li><strong>上传到Codabench:</strong> 点击\"提交\"按钮，上传您的zip文件</li>\n        <li><strong>等待处理:</strong> 平台会自动处理您的提交</li>\n        <li><strong>查看结果:</strong> 处理完成后，结果将显示在排行榜上</li>\n    </ol>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;\">\n    <strong>⚠️ 重要注意事项:</strong>\n    <ul>\n        <li>确保zip中只包含一个CSV文件</li>\n        <li>zip中不要包含文件夹</li>\n        <li>确保CSV格式正确</li>\n        <li>预测顺序必须正确</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📥 下载</h2>\n<div style=\"background: #e7f3ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n    <h3>可用下载</h3>\n    <ul>\n        <li><strong>测试数据集</strong> - 预处理后的测试数据</li>\n        <li><strong>示例预测</strong> - 展示正确格式的示例CSV文件</li>\n        <li><strong>示例代码</strong> - 用于生成提交CSV的Python脚本</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>",
      "index": 1
    }
